channel.title: Half-Life Preliminary Findings CD
channel.description: All the footage from the promotional Preliminary Findings CD of Half-Life made into one movie as a sort of Making Of. The disc contains gameplay movies, interviews with several Valve employees, screen shots and tons of game info. 10 cool minutes.
